{"tid":1768011,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［今次絕非人血饅頭］取代和你宵 【宵埋你】 上線啦!","createTime":"2019-12-03T17:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T02:06:16.000Z","uid":202761,"like":50,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"fe783d378f188b19c865ac6d2f885dcbda800c17","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T17:59:08.000Z","msg":"大家好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地係 <span style=\"color: gold;\">「宵埋你」</span> 相信大家如果有追開po 都知舊「和你宵」嘅人涉嫌食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以我地團隊決定取代佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">振興黃色經濟圈</span><br />\n<br />\n我地會舉辦類似「和你宵」既年宵活動，直接係第二區進行， <span style=\"color: red;\">我地唔係舊「和你宵」嘅人，亦都同佢地無任何關係 唔會用佢地嘅資金</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地只會收定額租金，唔會競投。</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> <span style=\"color: gold;\">絕對透明</span></strong></span><br />\n我地會公佈數字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />扣除成本有賺錢嘅話我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: gold;\">利潤我地會用特別嘅方法取代藍店生意，同埋創造更多就業機會，請番手足番工；或者全數捐出</span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>場地方面</strong></span></span><br />\n我地暫時傾緊一個新場地 大概40萬尺，可以有食物攤位、娛樂攤位、音樂會、乾濕貨等等 <span style=\"color: gold;\">真正有得食有得玩又有得chill</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如大場地傾唔成，我地會轉向唔同地區既細場地。暫時有銅鑼灣1.5萬尺，荃灣7層3萬尺等等。<br />\n<br />\n我地同時會搵公信力人士去監察 例如議員 KOL等等<br />\n<br />\n我地會盡快發佈所有消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎大家入黎公海 集思廣益 <span style=\"color: gold;\">一齊傾個真正屬於你 屬於香港人嘅黃色年宵出黎</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公海：@newyearplan2020<br />\nChannel發佈消息： @newyearplan<br />\n檔主申請表：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/qupAvm5peRDotHheA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FqupAvm5peRDotHheA&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDUBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=e22f169e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/qupAvm5peRDotHheA</a><br />\n<br />\n有任何疑問可聯絡admin： @wolesiu2020"},{"pid":"f6e18ef275c3a5bae09468670e6d86084c896812","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:00:02.000Z","msg":"自推10下"},{"pid":"e05807e1a3f57bd9b7ef68705a829e175c54a40e","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:00:13.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"31d7d9acd2716f2c1d9c6c636a24ed4533096dc4","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:00:35.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"f85646db786088df39c0a78bfc80da03ee66b57c","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:00:45.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"9458da8c27a8be741cef0fa37ff06adf0a85ee12","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:00:55.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"52837a757981e2e07dfad391addfdd9a3d88b9dc","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:01:13.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"69e19a788648afbf39122394aaad05e7008d944c","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:01:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"30b67272bb19ce8c106ec76186d4a220ac7c2cbd","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:01:33.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"0498f84ea30732375c80ced5709f6c9b51bf5639","tid":1768011,"uid":202761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:01:44.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"89452ae8809c1baeee070e42d311a13d362e5954","tid":1768011,"uid":20